A diesel generator is a machine that generates electricity using a diesel engine. Diesel generators are used to provide backup power in case of mains power failure, or as the primary source of power when there is no main power grid or the main power is unreliable. [http://www.fgwilsonmiami.com/cgi-bin/stores/fgwlive/censtore.cgi?lg=english&page=fgw-products.html&cart_id=5397099.30170&department=anyany&affiliate=&le=&lp=&sct=432 Diesel generators] range from 1kVA to 2000kVA and can be configured based on the requirement.